Package net.dnddev.factions.base

Location for the base entities that make up Factions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Claim
    Used to represent an area claimed by a Faction.
    Faction
    The base entity that this API is based around.
    FactionStore
    The base system to store Factions and the areas that they have claimed.
    Messageable
    Represents anything that is able to receive a string based message.
    Purchasable
    There are several things that are able to be purchased within Factions.
    User
    The base entity for anyone who interacts with the Faction system.
    Warp
    A location set by Factions to be able to easily teleport to.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Claim2D
    The two-dimensional implementation of a Claim.
    Claim3D
    The three-dimensional implementation of a Claim.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Faction.Type
    Represents the purpose for each Faction.
